headline.main: No. 5 South Carolina Tops Mississippi State for SEC Title
headline.print_headline: No. 5 South Carolina Tops Mississippi State for SEC Title

lead_paragraph: A'ja Wilson believes No. 5 South Carolina proved it's not only the best in the Southeastern Conference, but one of the best in the country and a major threat in the NCAA Tournament.
